This is a project about dogs. The project is a blog where users can read posts and leave comments. The blog is written in php language, in the oop system.
Some functionalities of the project. Sign up and enter. Once users register, users can then leave comments on some posts, reply comments. Privilege to vote on posts.
The vote is calculated based on the sum of all the votes, and gets the sum that I have shown in happy or sad smiley.
When the user is logged in, a rating in the form of a star will be displayed on each post on which he voted The highest rating is five stars. Paginate is created.
The entire logic of the project is in the admin panel that communicates with the database where all the data is stored. CRUD system for all data. 
Users or guests can search for posts via categories or tags. And to search via live_ajax_bar.

